  <summary date="2021-04-09T17:49:06Z" status="Introduced in House">Highways Coronavirus Relief Act

This bill temporarily increases the federal share of funding to 100% for certain federal-aid highway projects.

The bill applies to existing and unliquidated obligations and those made after enactment through September 30, 2021, with specified exceptions.</summary>
